body_html: Current questions for me where from "tensorflow.python.framework.errors.OutOfRangeError: Nan in summary histogram for: HistogramSummary". Is nan out of range? Why I am getting a OutOfRangeError when I increase number of examples? Maybe a message like "Your learning rate is too big for finding local minimum" (what is the real problem?) would be more helpful?
